data.description: Welcome to Belleau Lake, a beautiful 200-acre lake surrounded by over 150 acres of conservation land to be explored alone or as a family or group. In addition to boating, fishing, and swimming, members can also enjoy the association's park, pavilion, beaches, and trails used for hiking and ATVs in summer and snowmobiles in winter. This adorable well-maintained cape is only a brisk walk to the sandy beach and a short drive to the association boat launch. It comfortably sleeps 8 and has beautiful laminate floors, stainless steel appliances and a Harman pellet stove to warm up on chilly nights. Off the dining room, there is a slider to an inviting deck in the back yard for grilling and fun summer meals. Full dry basement for storage or to finish and well-constructed 2-car detached garage make this property a great value. Sold mostly furnished.
